00:56:46,200 --> 00:56:49,160
Something had to go.

1294
00:56:49,160 --> 00:56:52,440
Subcortical function, this is a very corticocentric course.

1295
00:56:52,440 --> 00:56:54,840
Most of the course will deal with the cortex.

